Date: 20010727
Short: yasjoinsunicode
Title: YAS to Join the Unicode Consortium

<p>Thanks to sponsorship from <a
href="http://www.netthink.co.uk">NetThink</a>, Yet Another Society
will be joining the <a href="http://www.unicode.org">Unicode
Consortium</a>. Perl will be the first programming language to be
represented in the Unicode Consortium. This allows us to stay at the
cutting edge of Unicode development. Simon Cozens, Larry Wall and
Jarkko Hietaniemi will be the representatives for YAS at the Unicode
Consortium.</p>
